@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@staffRole = STAFF
@staffId = demo-staff
@jobId = REPLACE_JOB_ID
@productId = REPLACE_PRODUCT_ID
@variantId = REPLACE_VARIANT_ID

### Create workshop job (STAFF+)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/workshop/jobs
Content-Type: application/json
X-Staff-Role: {{staffRole}}
X-Staff-Id: {{staffId}}

{
  "customerName": "Alex Rider",
  "bikeDescription": "Trek Domane, brake rub",
  "notes": "Customer wants same-day if possible"
}

### Add PART line (STAFF+)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/workshop/jobs/{{jobId}}/lines
Content-Type: application/json
X-Staff-Role: {{staffRole}}
X-Staff-Id: {{staffId}}

{
  "type": "PART",
  "productId": "{{productId}}",
  "variantId": "{{variantId}}",
  "qty": 1,
  "unitPricePence": 1299
}

### Add LABOUR line (STAFF+)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/workshop/jobs/{{jobId}}/lines
Content-Type: application/json
X-Staff-Role: {{staffRole}}
X-Staff-Id: {{staffId}}

{
  "type": "LABOUR",
  "description": "Brake alignment and test ride",
  "qty": 1,
  "unitPricePence": 2500
}

### Finalize job -> basket (STAFF+)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/workshop/jobs/{{jobId}}/finalize
Content-Type: application/json
X-Staff-Role: {{staffRole}}
X-Staff-Id: {{staffId}}

{}

